# pmi-workers configuration moved to the platform-root single source of truth:
#   /Users/reid/micah/pmi_data_platform/.env
#
# This file is kept only as a pointer; pmi-workers inherits all settings from
# pmi-core (no service-specific Settings class today).
#
# pmi-workers specifically reads:
#   - PMI_WORKERS_DEFAULT_INDEX (which index `run-job score` ticks by default)
# Plus everything pmi-core needs (PMI_DB_*, PMI_MLFLOW_*, OPENAI_API_KEY, PMI_LOG_LEVEL).
#
# Bootstrap a fresh checkout:
#   cp pmi_data_platform/.env.example pmi_data_platform/.env
